name: Little Less Littoral than the Last (LLLttL)
description:
Original footage from timelapse video shot from a ferry boat in 2016 in the Hakone region of Japan. Put thru a few effects and things. I wanted to make something a little less literal than the last video minted. This piece is inspired in part by @letsglitchit and distortgill

H.264 (x264), 30 FPS PFR
AAC (CoreAudio), Stereo
AC3, Stereo
